'''''Sivaa''''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[BFF-1 bulk freighter/Legends|BFF-1 bulk freighter]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. As the [[Battle on the Frontier]] drew to a close, Freighter ''Sivaa'' escorted [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate]] ''[[Gaarni]]'' to replace the battle-weary Nebulon-B escort frigate ''[[Ludwick]]''. The ''Gaarni's'' task force arrived to relieve [[Grand Admiral/Legends|Grand Admiral]] [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo/Legends|Thrawn's]] initial invasion force sent to establish [[XQ1 Platform|Space Station]] ''[[NL-1]]'' in the [[Pakuuni system/Legends|Pakuuni system]]. ''Sivaa'' brought in fresh supplies for the platform.

